metadata.name: ETHRoom Denver // Genesis
metadata.description:
This key grants you exclusive access to our high-profile Denver Genesis event, where you'll connect with the brightest minds in blockchain and crypto. But that's not all - as part of a limited group of like-minded individuals shaping the future of the industry, you'll also receive special perks like premium exclusive merch and entry into our raffle. (Don't forget the POAPs)

And because we know your time is valuable, we've streamlined the ticketing process to make it quick and easy to secure your spot. Don't miss out on this opportunity to join an elite community of crypto pioneers.

Get your ETHROOMDAO Genesis Ticket today and take the first step towards an unparalleled DAO experience!
